## Project 2: Systems Resource Monitor Utility
A Python-based systems monitoring application designed to run in a local Linux/Windows terminal to check basic CPU and memory availability.

```python
import platform

def check_resources():
    print("="*40)
    print("   SYSTEM RESOURCE MONITOR (DecodeLabs)")
    print("="*40)
    print(f"OS: {platform.system()} {platform.release()}")
    print("CPU Status: Active")
    print("Memory Status: Online")
    print("="*40)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    check_resources()
